summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 41W, page 112 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone the property located at approximately 1601 East Jefferson Street from Single Family 5000 (SF 5000) zone to Lowrise-3 (L-3) zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Mel Streeter, C.F. 298647)
